[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    172[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    173[0m:[38;5;10m[49m This sentence reads slightly more like a regulatory document than an engineer explaining something. The parenthetical with three acronyms/terms in a row (De Novo, 510(k), SaMD) is dense.
