[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    212[0m:[38;5;10m[49m | 2 | HIGH | Architecture | Architecture Diagram, Code walkthrough | No DLQ or error handling for failed SageMaker calls. GPU cold starts (2-5 min) cause Lambda timeouts. Lost triage requests mean potentially urgent lesions never get prioritized. | Add SQS DLQ for failed invocations. Write `PENDING_INFERENCE` status to DynamoDB on failure. Implement scheduled retry. Alert on DLQ depth > 0. |
